Interface OptimizationService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    OptimizationServiceImpl

    public interface OptimizationService
    OptimizationConfiguration Service API This service will provide all the incoming requests associated with all related OptimizationConfiguration operations, delivering the appropriate responses.
